                        search) overwrites this container's innerHTML, so these
                        cards disappear on their own with no JS cleanup needed. %>
                    <% for (let i = 0; i < 12; i++) { %>
                    <div class="col-6 col-sm-4 col-md-3 p-2 skeleton-cell">
